metadata.name: GREEDY
metadata.description:
"GREEDY" is a digital art piece in a collection that explores the theme of demons and sins through abstract, darkly-colored works. 

This particular piece focuses on the sin of greed, and depicts a demon representing this sin in a way that is meant to be unsettling and unsettling. 

The use of dark colors and distorted forms adds to the piece's ominous and otherworldly feel, evoking a sense of danger and mystery.
